abstract: Doctors determine that no further medical treatment is possible for Mississippi Rep Alan Nunnelee after finding new tumor.
lead_paragraph: Doctors have found a new tumor in Representative Alan Nunnelee and told him no further medical treatment is possible, his spokesman said Friday.

headline.main: Mississippi: New Tumor Found in Congressman
